<html>
    <body>
        <p>${currentDate}</p>
        <p>
            A Notice of Termination (NOT) requesting termination of coverage under EPA's Construction General Permit (CGP)
            for stormwater discharges from ${form.formData.projectSiteInformation.siteName}, ${form.formData.projectSiteInformation.siteAddress},
            for NPDES ID NPDES ID: ${form.formSet.npdesId}, has been prepared by ${form.formData.operatorInformation.preparer.firstName}
            ${form.formData.operatorInformation.preparer.lastName} (${form.formData.operatorInformation.preparer.email})
            with you listed as the Certifier. This NOT will not be submitted to the EPA until it is certified by you.
            Please log in to the NPDES Electronic Reporting Tool (NeT) to review and take action on this form.
            NeT can be accessed from: <a href="${applicationLink}">${applicationLink}</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
            Once logged in, you can use the filtering capability to find the NOI for certification.  After you have
            completed your review, follow the steps presented on the screen to certify the submission. If you choose not
            to certify the NOI, select "Reject", enter a Reason for Rejection, and submit.  This action will route the
            rejected form back to the Preparer in NeT, and generate an email notifying the Preparer that the form has
            been rejected, your reason for rejection, and instructions to resubmit as needed.
        </p>
        <p>
            You will receive an email informing you once your revised coverage under the CGP is active. For guidance about
            this process, please visit: <a href="${eReporting}">${eReporting}</a>.  For more information
            about the CGP, including a copy of the permit, please visit: <a href="${stormwaterCgp}">${stormwaterCgp}</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
            If you have questions about this email or about NeT CGP, please refer to the NeT Help Center
            at <a href="${netHelpCenter}">${netHelpCenter}</a> or e-mail ${npdesEmail} for assistance.
            If you have questions regarding the permit requirements of EPA’s CGP, please contact EPA at ${raEmail}.
        </p>
        <p>
            This is an automated notification; please do not reply to this email.
        </p>
    </body>
</html>